author: Alexander Aaltonen
text:
Love this AF outlet! Well-planned and efficient layout considering its small size. The staff is super friendly and always greet you with a smile. Occasionally free treats are also offered to members!

The gym itself includes all the essential machines and equipment. The facilities are also well maintained -- always feels neat and clean here!

As the gym is quite small, it might get quite crowded, but usually I go very late when there's less people, so not a problem at all for me ðŸ™Œ

author: Lucien Lim
text: A well-equipped 24h gym that is clean and well maintained. The equipment look new and function well. The only issue I see here is the lack of wheelchair access (no lift available), as the gym is divided into 3 floors accessible by staircase.

author: Gary Ang
text: This is a relatively small gym, it has a different feel of the gym compared to other AF. I actually like the lay out of the gym, it seems a little bit cramped but the usage of the space is excellent! Lighting was good at level 2 and 3. Love it when a gym has diverging lats pull down. Was greeted warmly by the staff when I entered. Parking can be tricky around geylang and MRT is around 10-15min walk away.

author: Thomas Lee
text: Great gym. Small(but all you need available), equipment packed efficiently and friendly staff.

author: Moriba Konate
text:
Pros: gym is well equipped with all sorts of machines (if thatâ€™s your thing) and the people are super nice

Cons: space is quite tight with everything on top of each other. Only 2 squats racks which are in front of each other and quite close to the ceiling. The bar was touching the top beam as I was shoulder pressing.

author: Alex Neville
text: Great small gym. Made excellent use of the space. Staff are generally lovely and the equipment is in good condition. It's super convenient for me and is right next to plenty of good eateries to pack back on the calories you burn off!

author: WS Yong
text: This AF has probably the friendliest staff I've encountered so far in SG, owner is friendly too; even though it's not the one I signed up under, and also group classes. Not that crowded either.

author: Lyn Sarah MY
text:
Great service by Elyana and Alif, welcoming and friendly.

1st time in the gym.  Even though it is a bit narrow but makes up for the 3 floors, clean and nice scent.  Equipment spaced out nicely.

Went for the Bodypump class by Instructor Mon on Thursday evening.  Informative and jovial.  A lot of strength and stamina considering he taught 2 classes back to back.  ðŸ˜…

Will come back.

author: leyon wong
text: The gym has adequate equipments and staff are friendly

author: Enzo Javier
text: One of the best AF gyms, 3 stories - machines, cardio equip, free weights, squat racks, open area, & accessories. Clean bathroom / locker area & accessible sanitation sprays shows that this joint is well managed.

author: WanderWithWit
text: It gave me with a surprise that this gym 3 levels can actually be quite well equipped and has a pent floor area for classes and stretching. Nice!!

author: trancegravity84
text: One of the most well equipped gym even though it is spread across 3 floors. Pleasant layout. Nice.

author: ARS
text: staffs are nice and cheerful. Area size is not that big as compared to other branches but it has a radiant atmosphere.

author: usman shaikh
text:
Have never been there but its an international brand and heared good vibes about them.
Seeing is beleiving, but here experiencing is rather appropriate.
I do recommend based on there credibility and information heared plus written on their website.

author: Tayrius Low
text: Nice place. 3 levels high. Went to a bodypump class with an instructor called Alex Chiew. Great experience.

author: Sham Sath
text: Hanz was very friendly and helpful. Excited to be a part of this gym!

author: Christina Chew
text: Friendly and good place to gym. Great group classes and staff.

author: Jovan Malik
text: Hanz was very helpful and informative in assisting with the sign up. Look forward to working out here

author: jayapalmani jayapalmani
text: Perfect

author: Lee Keng Jie
text: Hanz is providing very good service and patiently explain on the terms. Overall a very good job.

author: jesper chong
text: hanz was very friendly and was very helpful with reactivating my account

author: Emmanuel Guedia Letchindjio
text: Well equipped but could use more equipment for lower back

author: JH soh
text: Poor ventilation upstairs, feels like a sauna

author: Sky Lee
text: Hope it can add more rack barbell for bench press and squat

author: Danny H
text: Well equipped

author: Mac Mac
text: Friendly staff

author: Steve Wee
text: Thank you for your review! :) It means a lot to us, we hope that you enjoyed your workout with us!
